{"tid":2130100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞撚到係街曬住食飯都仲有人講：冇計啦，政府無錯㗎","createTime":"2020-07-29T04:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T06:35:00.000Z","uid":45123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef604fdcf0ac1ecfbe6cec886e94743d18640cd6","tid":2130100,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:41:51.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲真係冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705a6dc31cfae0e3d3f74b19902c279dff2864de","tid":2130100,"uid":292416,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ef604fdcf0ac1ecfbe6cec886e94743d18640cd6","tid":2130100,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:41:51.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲真係冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"中國人知道自己是卑劣的奴隸，如果有人按照他們真實的階級身份對待他們，他們就會暗中佩服，覺得這些人有眼力，對其他事情的判斷，大概也沒錯。如果有人尊重中國人，把他們當做有靈魂有良知有廉恥的生物，中國人根據同樣的理由，就會懷疑這些人的判斷力，包括對其他跟中國無關事情的判斷力，不但不會信任和追隨這些人，反而會覺得這些人是適合欺騙掠奪的對象。<br />\n因此，中國人總是會落入比原來更壞的主人手中。只有邪惡的統治者才能讓中國人心悅誠服，同時大大降低他們對世界其他部分本來必然會造成的破壞。<br />\n<br />\n梳士：<a href=\"https://medium.com/@LiuZhongjing/一點人生的經驗-如何統治中國和造福世界-624ddd57506f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40LiuZhongjing%2F%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%93%E9%A9%97-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%B5%B1%E6%B2%BB%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%92%8C%E9%80%A0%E7%A6%8F%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-624ddd57506f&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6RnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=5807030c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@LiuZhongjing/一點人生的經驗-如何統治中國和造福世界-624ddd57506f</a>"},{"pid":"719c2304d872a090fb6e6e39b1916170d1cdfd0f","tid":2130100,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"705a6dc31cfae0e3d3f74b19902c279dff2864de","tid":2130100,"uid":292416,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"